# FormFlow 백엔드 dev 유닛 — Iwinv 서버 dev 인스턴스 (prod formflow.service 와 포트·경로 분리).
# SPRING_PROFILES_ACTIVE=dev 는 /opt/formflow-dev/.env 에서 지정한다.
[Unit]
Description=FormFlow Backend (dev)
After=network.target mysqld.service redis.service

[Service]
Type=simple
EnvironmentFile=/opt/formflow-dev/.env
Environment=JAVA_HOME=/usr/lib/jvm/java-17-openjdk
ExecStart=/usr/lib/jvm/java-17-openjdk/bin/java -jar /opt/formflow-dev/formflow.jar --server.port=9001
Restart=on-failure
User=root

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
